  "html": "<article class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n\n  <!-- Hero Intro -->\n  <header class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-flame to-sunglow text-white p-8 rounded-2xl mb-8\">\n    <h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4 leading-tight\">Mosquito Repellent for Cuba: What Actually Works Against Those Hungry Devils</h1>\n    <p class=\"text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-95\">Look, Cuban mosquitoes aren't playing around. Between the humidity, the standing water after afternoon rains, and whatever genetic rage these things have inherited — your family needs serious protection. Not the watered-down stuff from the pharmacy shelf. We're talking industrial-strength defense that survives a summer in Santiago without losing potency. This guide breaks down what's worth shipping and what's just expensive perfume for bugs.</p>\n  </header>\n\n  <!-- Context Section -->\n  <section class=\"prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-8\">\n    <p>Here's the thing about mosquito repellent that most people don't think through: you need <em>different</em> products for different jobs. Skin repellent keeps them from biting you directly. Clothing treatment keeps them from biting <em>through</em> your clothes (yes, they do that). And for Cuba specifically, you want products that can handle 90% humidity without sweating off in twenty minutes.</p>\n    \n    <p>The three main active ingredients worth knowing about: DEET (the OG, proven for decades, some people don't love the smell), Picaridin (newer, doesn't damage plastics, easier on sensitive skin), and Permethrin (only for clothes and gear — never skin — but kills mosquitoes on contact). A smart package to Cuba includes at least two of these three.</p>\n    \n    <p>One more reality check: dengue, Zika, and chikungunya are all transmitted by mosquitoes in Cuba. This isn't about comfort — it's about keeping your family healthy. The products below are what I'd actually send to my own tías.</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Quick Answer Callout -->\n  <aside class=\"bg-sunglow/10 border-2 border-sunglow p-6 rounded-xl my-8\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-0 mb-3\">The Short Version</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4\">Send the <strong>Sawyer Permethrin</strong> ($$) for treating clothes plus <strong>Repel 100</strong> ($) for skin. That combo covers both bases, ships easily, and gives your family protection that actually lasts in tropical conditions. The Permethrin stays effective through 6 washes — which in Cuba might be two months of use.</p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001ANQVYU?tag=veguitas-20\" class=\"mt-4 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">See the Sawyer Permethrin on Amazon</a>\n  </aside>\n\n  <!-- Section: Clothing & Gear Treatments -->\n  <section class=\"mb-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6\">Clothing Treatments: The Secret Weapon Nobody Talks About</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6\">Permethrin is what the military uses. You spray it on clothes, let it dry, and it kills mosquitoes that land on the fabric. It's not a repellent — it's an insecticide. Huge difference. And it survives multiple washes.</p>\n\n    <!-- Product Card: Sawyer Permethrin 24oz -->\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\">\n        <div class=\"md:w-1/3\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71BgXKIOvzL._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"Sawyer Products Premium Permethrin 24oz - Best Mosquito Repellent in Bulk for clothing treatment\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"md:w-2/3\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white m-0\" data-asin=\"B001ANQVYU\">Sawyer Permethrin 24oz Spray</h3>\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">4.6★</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-flame font-semibold mb-3\">$$</p>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4\">This is the size to send. The 24oz bottle treats roughly 4-5 outfits and lasts through 6 washes or 42 days of wear. In Cuban heat where you're changing clothes constantly? That's real value. Treats uniforms, work clothes, mosquito nets — anything fabric.</p>\n          <p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white\">VERDICT: Best value for families. One bottle protects everyone.</p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001ANQVYU?tag=veguitas-20\" class=\"mt-4 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">Check Price on Amazon</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Product Card: Sawyer Permethrin 4.5oz -->\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\">\n        <div class=\"md:w-1/3\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61-sPgzpE7L._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"Sawyer Products Premium Permethrin 4.5oz travel size\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"md:w-2/3\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white m-0\" data-asin=\"B001ANQVZE\">Sawyer Permethrin 4.5oz Travel Size</h3>\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">4.6★</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-flame font-semibold mb-3\">$</p>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4\">Same formula, smaller bottle. Good for one person's wardrobe or if you're adding it to a care package with limited space. Treats about 2 outfits. Nice to include when shipping weight is tight.</p>\n          <p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white\">VERDICT: Perfect add-on. Toss one in every package.</p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001ANQVZE?tag=veguitas-20\" class=\"mt-4 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">Check Price on Amazon</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Product Card: Sawyer Permethrin Large Spray -->\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\">\n        <div class=\"md:w-1/3\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81drsTLaouL._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"Sawyer Products Premium Permethrin large bulk spray bottle\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"md:w-2/3\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white m-0\" data-asin=\"B07CD9NFB4\">Sawyer Permethrin Bulk Size</h3>\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">4.6★</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-flame font-semibold mb-3\">$$$</p>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4\">The big boy. If you're sending to a larger household or want to treat mosquito nets, curtains, and hammocks too, this makes sense. Otherwise the 24oz hits the sweet spot better for most families.</p>\n          <p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white\">VERDICT: Overkill for most. Get it if treating furniture or nets.</p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07CD9NFB4?tag=veguitas-20\" class=\"mt-4 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">Check Price on Amazon</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Section: Maximum Strength Skin Repellents -->\n  <section class=\"mb-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6\">Maximum Strength Skin Repellents: When You Need the Big Guns</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6\">DEET at 98-100% concentration sounds intense, but it's what actually works in heavy mosquito areas. These aren't daily-use products — they're for fishing trips, rural visits, or places where dengue is actively circulating. Ten hours of protection means you apply once and forget it.</p>\n\n    <!-- Product Card: Repel 100 4oz -->\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\">\n        <div class=\"md:w-1/3\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61LXfxfWwyL._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"Repel 100 Insect Repellent 4oz Pump Spray - 98% DEET maximum protection\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"md:w-2/3\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white m-0\" data-asin=\"B004H89KFC\">Repel 100 Insect Repellent (4oz)</h3>\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">4.6★</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-flame font-semibold mb-3\">$</p>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4\">98.11% DEET. This is pharmaceutical-grade mosquito warfare. One small pump application covers exposed skin for up to 10 hours — even through sweating, even in humidity. The 4oz size is ideal for shipping: enough to last months with sensible use, light enough not to kill your shipping costs.</p>\n          <p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white\">VERDICT: The gold standard. Send this for serious protection.</p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B004H89KFC?tag=veguitas-20\" class=\"mt-4 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">Check Price on Amazon</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Product Card: Repel 100 1oz -->\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\">\n        <div class=\"md:w-1/3\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71HAn5L7DpL._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"Repel 100 Insect Repellent 1oz pocket size spray\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"md:w-2/3\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white m-0\" data-asin=\"B000LGN3Z2\">Repel 100 Pocket Size (1oz)</h3>\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">4.6★</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-flame font-semibold mb-3\">$</p>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4\">Same 98% DEET formula in a pocket-sized bottle. Fits in a purse, backpack, or guayabera pocket. Great for someone who's constantly on the move — guagua drivers, field workers, anyone who can't predict when they'll need it.</p>\n          <p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white\">VERDICT: Perfect portable backup. Tuck a few into any package.</p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000LGN3Z2?tag=veguitas-20\" class=\"mt-4 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">Check Price on Amazon</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Product Card: Ben's 100 2-Pack -->\n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6\">\n        <div class=\"md:w-1/3\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71mXT4opT0L._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"Ben's 100 DEET Tick and Insect Repellent 2-Pack alcohol-free formula\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"md:w-2/3\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white m-0\" data-asin=\"B0738NCJMH\">Ben's 100 DEET 2-Pack (3.4oz each)</h3>\n            <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium\">4.5★</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-flame font-semibold mb-3\">$$</p>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4\">The key difference: alcohol-free formula. If someone in the family has sensitive skin or doesn't love the chemical smell of standard DEET products, Ben's is noticeably gentler. Same 10-hour protection. The 2-pack is great for splitting between household members.</p>\n          <p class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white\">VERDICT: Best for sensitive skin. Slightly less harsh feel.</p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0738NCJMH?tag=veguitas-20\" class=\"mt-4 inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-flame text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">Check Price on Amazon</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Section: Gentler Alternatives -->\n  <section class=\"mb-12\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6\">Gentler Alternatives: Picaridin & Plant-Based Options</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6\">Not everyone wants to douse themselves in DEET daily. Picaridin offers similar protection with a lighter feel — it won't damage plastics or synthetic fabrics, and it's easier on kids. Plant-based options work too, just for shorter periods.</p>\n\n    <!-- Head-to-Head: Picaridin Options -->\n    <div class=\"my-8\">\n      <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4\">Picaridin Showdown: Spray vs. Lotion vs. Continuous</h3>\n      <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        \n        <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71Z+P7a34UL._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"Sawyer Picaridin Pump Spray 2-Pack\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700 mb-4\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\" data-asin=\"B07BSM6WTY\">Sawyer Picaridin Spray 2-Pack</h4>\n          <p class=\"text-flame font-semibold text-sm mb-2\">$$</p>\n          <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium\">4.5★</span>\n          <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-3\">3oz pump bottles. 20% Picaridin gives 12 hours of protection. No greasy feel, dries clear. Won't melt watch bands or sunglasses.</p>\n          <p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-2\">Best for: Daily use, easy sharing</p>\n          <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07BSM6WTY?tag=veguitas-20\" class=\"mt-3 inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-flame text-white text-sm font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">View on Amazon</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71Nf8TQw98L._AC_UL320_.jpg\" alt=\"Sawyer Picaridin Lotion 4oz\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-48 object-contain bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700 mb-4\">\n          <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2\" data-asin=\"B00VV5KRD8\">Sawyer Picaridin Lotion (4oz)</h4>\n          <p class=\"text-flame font-semibold text-sm mb-2\">$</p>\n       